<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Jordan luigal I kaih tiengleh,
 Hehpih gam vak hawih achun,
 Luigal gam Lalpa kawm achun,
 A In vakah chawl hitiu.

[V2]
 Aw, ka Lalpa zie hehpih gam hawih vak chu
 Chawlhna'n Na siem tai Na thisan ngei chun
 Kei gilo hin thisan zal in ka hun zuon
 Thisan a silthieng in ei chawlh sak in.

[V3]
 2. Zie chun Lalpa gam tiem achun,
 Ka ngaklah hi chawlh phat ding,
 Zie hinna hhing dailim achun,
 Bangtikleh ka chawl die aw !

[V4]
 3. Aw, van Jerusalem Thak khu,
 A hawih in a lopi ie,
 Ka nuktan tiengleh Lal Isu
 Na khawpi thak ei tun in.

[V5]
 4. Hukdampa kawm ka tun tiengleh,
 Lungkham kit ta puong ka ting,
 Buoina khel gam achun chawl in,
 Kiel lungzinna bei tan a.</lyrics>
<title>Jordan Luigal Ah</title>
<author>C.Z. Huala</author>
<hymn_number>227</hymn_number>
</song>